data.description: Explore this charming contemporary Cape Cod home situated in a tranquil, friendly Town of Poughkeepsie. Offering 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, this residence strikes a perfect balance between comfort and style.    Upon entry, you'll be welcomed by the airy and inviting atmosphere that flows throughout. The kitchen, with its eat-in design, serves as the heart of the home. Outfitted with sleek black stainless-steel appliances, it combines modern style with practicality. Tile flooring in the kitchen adds durability and easy maintenance.    The well-thought-out layout creates a harmonious blend of personal and communal spaces. Bedrooms are designed for relaxation and privacy, while the updated full and half baths feature contemporary fixtures in a clean, timeless design.    Outside, the property exudes tranquility, making it an ideal setting for enjoying the quiet neighborhood. Whether you're savoring your morning coffee on the porch or hosting gatherings in the backyard, the surroundings provide a serene backdrop.  Minute from train station.  Motivated Sellers!  This contemporary Cape Cod home delivers a tasteful and sophisticated living experience, with its modern amenities and thoughtful design. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
